  "type": "spell",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;magus 2, sorcerer/wizard 3, witch 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a pinch of rust)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one armored creature<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round/level (D)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Reflex partial; see text;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>Upon pointing at an armored foe, you cause all of the joints of the target's armor to stiffen as otherworldly chains wrap around the target. On a failed Reflex save, a target in heavy metal armor becomes staggered. A target in light or medium metal armor instead becomes entangled. <b>Target</b>s wearing no armor or nonmetallic armor are unaffected. If the target is wearing heavy metal armor and succeeds at its Reflex save, it becomes entangled instead of staggered; a target in light or medium metal armor that succeeds at its saving throw is unaffected by the spell.</p>\n</div>\n",
